      "message": "optional / just saying: in case the length of this line bothers you, or if we have more conditions in future, using switch might make this code more readable:\n\nswitch {\ncase matches(s.Name, names):\ncase matches(s.Rack, racks):\ncase matches(s.Datacenter, datacenters):\ndefault:\n  switches \u003d append(switches, s)\n}",
